Package dataTypes

Class McNemarsOutput

java.lang.Object
dataTypes.McNemarsOutput
public class McNemarsOutput
extends java.lang.Object
Represents output of McNemar's procedure. The procedure is use to judge the significance of the difference between correlated proportions.
Author:
Sudesh Agrawal (sudesh@utexas.edu). Last Updated: September 24, 2020.
